    "description": "<p>As an academic establishment since 1981, we are fully committed to our service policy that consistently thrives on providing quality and value-added educational courses and services to local and international students alike.</p>\n\n<p>We are fully committed towards the education process of all our students and in doing so we strive to achieve the highest quality standard in all aspects of our operations. In May 2010, TMC Academy received the 4-year EduTrust Certification awarded by the Committee for Private Education (CPE), a statutory board established under the Private Education Act with the legislative power to regulate the private education section in Singapore. </p>\n",
